{
  "stem": "26983.11",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Put it in a blanket, trampled on it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they were just crumbs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And sometimes the crumbs were [NON-ENGLISH], how you call it, [NON-ENGLISH] with--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, they were not edible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't eat it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, we couldn't eat it, but then what he gave us and even these few crumbs, they were tasteless, and we had to sell a few of these crumbs to get a few drops of salt, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he beat up people in the most-- the shouting of the poor Jews who were beaten by him, it's unforgettable.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was really a sadist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that was only the beginning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later on, it was worse and worse, because there was evacuation of all camps from the east, and they were brought to the west.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All the former concentration camps were over-- overfilled with prisoners.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I'm speaking of Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There came more and more transports.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then there came transports from Hungarian Jews and women.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was the so-called Munka Tabor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Munka Tabor is [INAUDIBLE] Hungarian working camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they came also by Todesmarsche and so on or by train to Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Mauthausen was overfilled.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some people went further on to [INAUDIBLE] and other camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they had to work in these under--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in mines.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this factory where they have-- where they produce parts of the firearms, the rockets, in horrible condition under the ground.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We, who were a little group of children, were lucky we were staying in Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At least not all of us went to a very severe work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sometimes we didn't went at all to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But slowly, we were losing weight and energy and even then we were transported to another camp in my Mauthausen, the so-called Zelt.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Zelt means--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A huge tent.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
